CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1772175649
OL,3,CChancellor urged to act as young
OL,4,Cpeople out of work or study nears one
OL,5,Cmillion
OL,7,FThe number of 16 to 24-year-olds in
OL,8,Fthe UK who are not in education,
OL,9,Femployment or training (NEET) rose
OL,10,Fagain in the final three months of
OL,11,Flast year.
OL,13,FOfficial estimates from the Office for
OL,14,FNational Statistics show that 957,000
OL,15,Fpeople in this age group were NEET
OL,16,Fbetween October and December - 12.8%
OL,17,Fof the total.
OL,19,FOf those, 547,000 said they were not
OL,20,Flooking for work.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1772175649
OL,3,CChancellor urged to act as young
OL,4,Cpeople out of work or study nears one
OL,5,Cmillion
OL,7,FA person is classified as NEET if they
OL,8,Fare either unemployed or economically
OL,9,Finactive - meaning they are not
OL,10,Fseeking a job or waiting to start one.
OL,11,FThe definition excludes anyone in
OL,12,Fschool, university, vocational
OL,13,Ftraining or an apprenticeship.
OL,15,FThe total has been rising steadily
OL,16,Fsince 2022. It previously peaked at
OL,17,Fmore than 1.2 million in 2012, in the
OL,18,Faftermath of the financial crisis,
OL,19,Fbefore falling to a pre-pandemic low
OL,20,Fof around 800,000 in early 2020.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1772175649
OL,3,CChancellor urged to act as young
OL,4,Cpeople out of work or study nears one
OL,5,Cmillion
OL,7,FThe latest figures will add to
OL,8,Fconcerns that those at the start of
OL,9,Ftheir working lives are being
OL,10,Fdisproportionately affected by the
OL,11,Fweakness of the labour market and are
OL,12,Fstruggling to make the transition from
OL,13,Feducation into employment.
OL,15,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1772175649
OL,3,CChancellor urged to act as young
OL,4,Cpeople out of work or study nears one
OL,5,Cmillion
OL,7,FThose who drift away from work or
OL,8,Fstudy are statistically more likely to
OL,9,Fdepend on benefits, experience poorer
OL,10,Fmental health and face a higher risk
OL,11,Fof contact with the criminal justice
OL,12,Fsystem.
OL,14,FThe Resolution Foundation, a think
OL,15,Ftank focussed on improving living
OL,16,Fstandards for low and middle income
OL,17,Fhouseholds, says the problem is
OL,18,Fbecoming urgent and the chancellor
OL,19,Fshould take action in her Spring
OL,20,FForecast next week.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1772175649
OL,3,CChancellor urged to act as young
OL,4,Cpeople out of work or study nears one
OL,5,Cmillion
OL,7,F"Britain is perilously close to having
OL,8,Fa million young people not in
OL,9,Feducation, employment or training for
OL,10,Fthe first time in 13 years," says
OL,11,FLouise Murphy, a senior economist at
OL,12,FResolution Foundation.
OL,14,FShe added: "Today's data adds to the
OL,15,Fpicture of a generation up against
OL,16,Freal and complex barriers to finding a
OL,17,Fgood job and improving their living
OL,18,Fstandards. But acting sooner rather
OL,19,Fthan later can help prevent these
OL,20,Fworrying trends becoming an entrenched
OL,21,Fcrisis."
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@\O]vD@LOU}D@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1772175649
OL,3,CChancellor urged to act as young
OL,4,Cpeople out of work or study nears one
OL,5,Cmillion
OL,7,FIt's not entirely clear why the number
OL,8,Fof NEETs has been rising.
OL,10,FResearch published last year by
OL,11,FResolution Foundation found that while
OL,12,Funemployment remains the most common
OL,13,Freason for being NEET, the largest
OL,14,Frecent increase has been among those
OL,15,Fwho are economically inactive due to
OL,16,Fdisability or ill health. Around one
OL,17,Fin four NEETs are now out of work and
OL,18,Fnot actively seeking employment for
OL,19,Fthis reason.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1772175649
OL,3,CChancellor urged to act as young
OL,4,Cpeople out of work or study nears one
OL,5,Cmillion
OL,7,FThe report also suggested that people
OL,8,Fwith fewer academic qualifications,
OL,9,Fpoor school attendance or identified
OL,10,Fspecial educational needs are
OL,11,Fsignificantly more likely to become
OL,12,FNEET.
OL,14,FIt found that 60% of those classified
OL,15,Fas NEET today have never worked - up
OL,16,Ffrom 42% in 2005. Almost half (44%) do
OL,17,Fnot claim any form of benefit support,
OL,18,Fand the UK's NEET rate is now higher
OL,19,Fthan the European average.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1772175649
OL,3,CChancellor urged to act as young
OL,4,Cpeople out of work or study nears one
OL,5,Cmillion
OL,7,FThe latest data comes just one week
OL,8,Fafter figures showed that youth
OL,9,Funemployment had reached 16.1% - its
OL,10,Fhighest level in a decade.
OL,12,FThe two measures sound similar but are
OL,13,Fsubtly different.
OL,15,FWhen youth unemployment rises, it
OL,16,Fmeans more people in this age group
OL,17,Fare actively looking for work but
OL,18,Fcannot find it.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1772175649
OL,3,CChancellor urged to act as young
OL,4,Cpeople out of work or study nears one
OL,5,Cmillion
OL,7,FWhen the NEET rate rises, it indicates
OL,8,Fa growing share are outside both work
OL,9,Fand education - and many (547,000) are
OL,10,Fnot actively seeking employment.
OL,12,FThe fact that both measures are rising
OL,13,Fat the same time is concerning.
OL,15,FThe government is rolling out its
OL,16,FYouth Guarantee scheme, which will
OL,17,Fprovide around 40,000 paid work
OL,18,Fplacements for 18 to 21-year-olds who
OL,19,Fhave been unemployed for more than 18
OL,20,Fmonths.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1772175649
OL,3,CChancellor urged to act as young
OL,4,Cpeople out of work or study nears one
OL,5,Cmillion
OL,7,FAlan Milburn, a former Health
OL,8,FSecretary under Tony Blair, has been
OL,9,Fasked to investigate why unemployment
OL,10,Fand inactivity among 16 to 24-year-
OL,11,Folds has risen and to recommend how
OL,12,Fbest to respond.
OL,14,FOne reason job prospects have worsened
OL,15,Fis that employers have cut back on
OL,16,Fgraduate recruitment. However, some
OL,17,Fargue that government policy may also
OL,18,Fbe contributing.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1772175649
OL,3,CChancellor urged to act as young
OL,4,Cpeople out of work or study nears one
OL,5,Cmillion
OL,7,FIn her 2024 Budget, the Chancellor
OL,8,Fstructured the increase in employer
OL,9,FNational Insurance contributions in a
OL,10,Fway that disproportionately affected
OL,11,Fbusinesses employing low-paid and part-
OL,12,Ftime staff.
OL,14,FThe minimum wage was also increased
OL,15,Fsignificantly, with the rate for 18 to
OL,16,F20-year-olds rising by close to 20%.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1772175649
OL,3,CChancellor urged to act as young
OL,4,Cpeople out of work or study nears one
OL,5,Cmillion
OL,7,FSince those changes took effect in
OL,8,FApril last year, employment in retail
OL,9,Fand hospitality - sectors that tend to
OL,10,Femploy large numbers of younger
OL,11,Fworkers - has fallen, although
OL,12,Feconomists caution that multiple
OL,13,Ffactors are likely to be influencing
OL,14,Fhiring.
OL,16,F"These are the sectors where young
OL,17,Fpeople tend to get their first job,"
OL,18,Fsaid Andy King, former Chief of Staff
OL,19,Fat the Office for Budget
OL,20,FResponsibility, last week.
OL,26,@xD@AOUyD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31513
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1772175649
OL,3,CChancellor urged to act as young
OL,4,Cpeople out of work or study nears one
OL,5,Cmillion
OL,7,FHe added: "Obviously there are many
OL,8,Fother factors at play, but this is one
OL,9,Fpolicy change you can identify that
OL,10,Fwould be expected to have a material
OL,11,Fimpact on youth unemployment."
OL,13,FThe Resolution Foundation is urging
OL,14,Fthe chancellor to expand the Youth
OL,15,FGuarantee and suspend its plan to
OL,16,Fequalise the minimum wage rates of
OL,17,Fyoung people and adults.
OL,26,@oD@KOUsD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31514
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1772175649
OL,3,CChancellor urged to act as young
OL,4,Cpeople out of work or study nears one
OL,5,Cmillion
OL,7,FMinisters argue that higher minimum
OL,8,Fwages boost incomes for younger
OL,9,Fworkers and that the Youth Guarantee
OL,10,Fscheme is intended to strengthen
OL,11,Fpathways into employment.
OL,13,FWork and Pensions Secretary Pat
OL,14,FMcFadden said: "Today's figures
OL,15,Funderline the long-term challenge we
OL,16,Fare facing. The number has been rising
OL,17,Fsince 2022, with the majority of that
OL,18,Fincrease occurring before July last
OL,19,Fyear,
OL,26,@vD@POU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31515
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1772175649
OL,3,CChancellor urged to act as young
OL,4,Cpeople out of work or study nears one
OL,5,Cmillion
OL,7,F"That's why tackling the crisis of
OL,8,Fopportunity facing too many young
OL,9,Fpeople is one of my top priorities. We
OL,10,Fare investing #1.5 billion to tackle
OL,11,Fyouth unemployment, backing businesses
OL,12,Fto hire young people by fully funding
OL,13,Fapprenticeships for SME's, creating
OL,14,F50,000 additional apprenticeships in
OL,15,Fpriority growth sectors and rolling
OL,16,Fout our Youth Guarantee, so every
OL,17,Fyoung person has the chance to earn or
OL,18,Flearn."
OL,26,@oD@AOUzD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/16
